http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Water-supply-to-be-hit-on-Tuesday/article14001960.ece

Water supply will be hit throughout the city on Tuesday (January 19) as the pumping to Cauvery 1st, 2nd , 3rd Stages and 4th Stage Phase I and II will be stopped from 11 a.m. to 3 p.m.A Bangalore Water Supply and Sewerage Board (BWSSB) release said that consequent to the repair works by Bescom authorities at their stations, power supply will be disrupted to Harohalli Cauvery Water Supply Pumping Station. BWSSB is also taking up emergency maintenance work at TK Halli, Harohalli and Tataguni Pumping Stations.